{
  "name": "血怒刺青 Blood Fury Tattoo",
  "type": "equipment",
  "img": "icons/tools/scribal/burnisher-tooth.webp",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"wordsection1\"><span style=\"font-family:Signika, sans-serif\">覆蓋區域：兩條肢體與軀幹</span></p><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"wordsection1\" style=\"MARGIN-BOTTOM:12pt\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">該魔法刺青用一根特殊的針製作，該刺青的形狀與顏色能夠喚起憤怒。</span><br /><em><strong>刺青同調。</strong></em><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">同調此物品時，你需要將針持握，並抵在你想要讓刺</span><span class=\"GramE\">青出現</span>的那處面板上。當同調完成時，針頭會化為墨水再變成刺青。若你與刺青的同調結束，刺青會消失，針頭會再次出現在你的位置中。<br /><em><strong>嗜血狂襲。</strong></em><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">刺</span><span class=\"GramE\">青具有</span>10<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">發充能，其在每天黎明時恢復所有已消耗的充能。當刺青在你的面板上時，你獲得以下增益：</span></p><ul><li><p class=\"wordsection1\" style=\"MARGIN-BOTTOM:12pt\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">當你以武器攻擊命中一個生物時，你可以消耗</span>1<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">發充能對目標造成額外的</span>[[/r 4d6]]<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">暗蝕傷害，同時你恢復數值等於所</span><span class=\"GramE\">造成黯蝕傷害</span>的生命值。</p></li><li><p class=\"wordsection1\" style=\"MARGIN-BOTTOM:12pt\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">當一個你可見的生物對你造成傷害時，你可以消耗</span>1<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">發充能並使用你的反應對那個生物發動一次近戰攻擊，這次攻擊的攻擊檢定具有優勢。</span></p></li></ul></div></div>",
